			<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=56136&amp;sid=a06302a746ae252f705ab2d2c2221151#56136"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Mar 24, 2004 1:01 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Re: weapons for a new age...</span></td>
				<td width="30%" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap" align="right"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=56136&amp;sid=a06302a746ae252f705ab2d2c2221151"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>     </td></tr></table></td>
